      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GENERAL FRANKY (1) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (29.94) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 515m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Deserves serious consideration. MEPUNGA EXPRESS (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (30.01) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Boasts four wins from six starts out of this box. A big run wouldn't surprise. MOONLIGHT MILLER (4) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd in a Grade 4 on February 26 over 515m at this track behind Prison Break beaten 2 lengths (29.74). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Expecting another good run. UNLEASH THE LION (6) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
